   Cupido, C. N., S African Natl Biodivers Inst, Compton Herbarium, ZA-7735 Cape Town, South Africa.
   Skvarla, J. J., Univ Oklahoma, Oklahoma Biol Survey, Norman, OK 73019 USA.
