Affiliation = {Lau, JA (Corresponding Author), Univ Calif Davis, Ctr Populat Biol, 1 Shields Ave, Davis, CA 95616 USA.
   Univ Calif Davis, Ctr Populat Biol, Davis, CA 95616 USA.
   Univ Virginia, Dept Biol, Charlottesville, VA 22904 USA.},
