Month = {FEB},
Abstract = {A taxonomic study of Campanula L. subgenera Megalocalyx Damboldt and
   Sicyocodon (Feer) Damboldt is presented here. Taxonomical,
   nomenclatural, morphological, chromosomal, geographic and ecological
   data are recorded for each taxon. Based on these data, one species is
   included in C. subgenus Sicyocodon and 12 in C. subgenus Megalocalyx. In
